{"title_page": "Axis Direct", "text_new": "\n\n{{notability|Companies|date=September 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox company\n| name = Axis Direct\n| type = [[Private company|Private]]\n| logo = File:AxisDirect_Official_Company_Logo.jpg\n| caption =   \n| foundation = 2011\n| founder = \n| location_city = [[Mumbai]], [[Maharashtra]]\n| location_country = [[India]]\n| area_served = \n| key_people =  B Gopkumar, <small>Managing Director & CEO</small><br/> Anand Shaha, <small>Executive Director</small><br/> Amit Golia, <small>Chief General Manager</small>\n| num_employees = 2,100+\n| revenue =  {{INRConvert|5.62|b}}\n| operating_income =  \n| net_income =  \n| assets = \n| equity = \n| industry = [[Brokerage firm|Stock Broker]]<br/>[[Financial Services]]\n| subsid =  \n| parent =  [[Axis Bank]] | products =  Equity, Derivatives, Mutual Fund, SIP, ETFs, Tax Savings, Fixed Income, IPO\n| homepage = [https://simplehai.axisdirect.in https://simplehai.axisdirect.in]\n}}\n\n'''Axis Direct''' is the flagship brand under Axis Securities Limited, a subsidiary of [[Axis Bank]] in [[India]]. Its main offices are in [[Mumbai]]. The company employs over 2,100 people.\n\n==History==\nIn 2010, Axis Sales Limited acquired approvals/registrations from the regulatory authorities for brokering business on [[stock exchange]]s. With the inclusion of retail brokering, the company was renamed Axis Securities and Sales Limited and its brokering business was branded Axis Direct in January 2011.\n\n==Products and services==\nAxis Direct provides a 3-in-1 Online Investment Account<ref>{{cite news|title=Axis Securities launches \u2018Axis Direct Investment Kit\u2019|url=http://www.thehindu.com/business/Industry/axis-securities-launches-axisdirect-investment-kit/article5677662.ece|accessdate=14 February 2017}}</ref> which is a combination of Axis Bank Savings and [[Demat account|Demat Accounts]] along with an Axis Direct trading account. Services:\n\n* Equities \u2013 Invest online in stocks of listed companies\n* Mutual Funds \u2013 Invest in mutual funds including equity, hybrid, tax saving or debt schemes from asset management companies\n* SIPs \u2013 Systematic investment plan that allows automated investments\n* IPOs - Invest in initial public offerings (IPO)\n* Derivatives \u2013 Hedge or speculate on the price movement of stocks or index through its derivative products viz. Futures and Options\n* Bonds, NCDs & Corporate FDs \u2013 Invest in fixed income instruments such as bonds, NCDs and Corporate FDs\n* ETFs - Invest in [[exchange-traded fund]]s\n* Value Added Services - Provides investing and trading ideas, along with financial tools and calculators, tax solutions, will planning and robot advisors.\n* MCX - Invest in bullion, metals, energy and agricultural commodities<ref>{{cite news|title=Axis Securities takes membership on MCX platform|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/newsscroll/axis-securities-takes-membership-on-mcx-platform/1233202|accessdate=22 January 2018|date=18 January 2018}}</ref>\n* NCDEX - Benefit from the bank's membership in NCDEX to invest in agriculture and non-agriculture commodities business, especially from semi-urban and rural India<ref>{{cite news|title=Axis Securities takes membership of NCDEX|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/axis-securities-takes-membershio-of-ncdex/articleshow/61918570.cms|accessdate=22 January 2018|date=5 December 2017}}</ref>\n* Equity smallcases - Invest in a curated basket of stocks based on a theme or market trend.<ref>{{cite news|title=March of ideas: Brokering firms line up thematic play|url=https://www.dnaindia.com/personal-finance/report-march-of-ideas-brokering-firms-line-up-thematic-play-2640850|date=24 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Mobile app==\nThe Mobile App allows customers buy and sell, watch their portfolio, track live markets and trade on the go. Mobile voice-based trading, the first in India to provide a touch-free stock trading experience.<ref>{{cite web|title=Press the Mic and Trade Your Stock with Voice Commands from this App|url=http://bwdisrupt.businessworld.in/article/Press-the-Mic-and-Trade-Your-Stock-with-Voice-Commands-from-this-App/24-05-2017-118838/|website=Business World|accessdate=1 June 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References and notes==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://simplehai.axisdirect.in Official Website]\n\n[[Category:Financial services companies of India]]\n[[Category:Indian companies established in 2011]]\n[[Category:Financial services companies based in Mumbai]]\n", "text_old": "\n\n{{notability|Companies|date=September 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox company\n| name = Axis Direct\n| type = [[Private company|Private]]\n| logo = File:AxisDirect_Official_Company_Logo.jpg\n| caption =   \n| foundation = 2011\n| founder = \n| location_city = [[Mumbai]], [[Maharashtra]]\n| location_country = [[India]]\n| area_served = \n| key_people =  Arun Thukral, <small>Managing Director & CEO</small><br/> Anand Shaha, <small>Executive Director</small><br/> Amit Golia, <small>Chief General Manager</small>\n| num_employees = 2,100+\n| revenue =  {{INRConvert|5.62|b}}\n| operating_income =  \n| net_income =  \n| assets = \n| equity = \n| industry = [[Brokerage firm|Stock Broker]]<br/>[[Financial Services]]\n| subsid =  \n| parent =  [[Axis Bank]] | products =  Equity, Derivatives, Mutual Fund, SIP, ETFs, Tax Savings, Fixed Income, IPO\n| homepage = [https://simplehai.axisdirect.in https://simplehai.axisdirect.in]\n}}\n\n'''Axis Direct''' is the flagship brand under Axis Securities Limited, a subsidiary of [[Axis Bank]] in [[India]]. Its main offices are in [[Mumbai]]. The company employs over 2,100 people.\n\n==History==\nIn 2010, Axis Sales Limited acquired approvals/registrations from the regulatory authorities for brokering business on [[stock exchange]]s. With the inclusion of retail brokering, the company was renamed Axis Securities and Sales Limited and its brokering business was branded Axis Direct in January 2011.\n\n==Products and servi